WEBVTT

01:39.430 --> 01:43.250
[Road to Success]

01:44.630 --> 01:47.950
[Episode 16]

01:48.140 --> 01:54.140
[Feiyang Fried Skewers]

01:48.560 --> 01:49.950
Brothers,

01:49.950 --> 01:51.710
we are in the top 500!

01:51.729 --> 01:54.450
Long live the top 500!

01:55.710 --> 01:56.640
I'm telling you,

01:56.640 --> 01:58.280
I've never been in the top 700 in my life.

01:58.280 --> 02:00.150
When my dad saw my report card yesterday,

02:00.150 --> 02:01.040
he laughed like crazy

02:01.040 --> 02:02.770
and asked me if he was dreaming.

02:03.070 --> 02:04.680
My mom cried tears of joy yesterday.

02:04.680 --> 02:05.870
My mom was happy too.

02:05.870 --> 02:08.440
That's why tonight's fried skewers
are at least twice the usual amount.

02:08.440 --> 02:11.030
Mom, we made it to the top 500!

02:11.030 --> 02:12.080
Auntie!

02:12.080 --> 02:14.310
We made it to the top 500!

02:14.310 --> 02:15.520
It's a happy occasion today, so eat more.

02:15.520 --> 02:16.310
It's on me.

02:16.310 --> 02:18.400
Okay, thank you, Auntie.

02:18.400 --> 02:20.240
-If we don't eat to our hearts' content tonight,
-Auntie, more kidneys please!

02:20.240 --> 02:21.079
nobody is allowed to leave!

02:21.079 --> 02:21.780
You said it!

02:21.800 --> 02:23.030
-You said it!
-I said it!

02:23.030 --> 02:24.520
Guys!

02:24.520 --> 02:26.890
We should raise a toast to Ms. Lin, right?

02:26.920 --> 02:27.540
Of course!

02:27.560 --> 02:28.630
-Of course!
-Come on!

02:28.630 --> 02:29.160
Definitely!

02:29.160 --> 02:32.030
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

02:31.030 --> 02:34.700
[Feiyang Fried Skewers]

02:37.540 --> 02:39.400
I think the skewers taste
even better today.

02:39.400 --> 02:39.910
Eat while it's hot.

02:39.910 --> 02:40.960
These mushrooms are delicious.

02:40.960 --> 02:42.710
-Do you know why?
-Why?

02:42.710 --> 02:44.150
-Because this is called a top 500 victory!
-My...

02:44.150 --> 02:45.079
These are top 500 celebration skewers!

02:45.079 --> 02:46.430
-Hold on.
-Who gave you face?

02:46.430 --> 02:47.310
Forget it. I won't hold it against you.

02:47.310 --> 02:48.800
Four hundred and what?

02:49.360 --> 02:50.590
-What is this?
-What?

02:52.910 --> 02:54.170
Wen Chengye posted it?

02:54.840 --> 02:56.710
Isn't this the manager of Yongchuan?

02:56.710 --> 02:57.370
That's him.

02:57.380 --> 02:58.610
Why is he with Coach?

02:58.870 --> 03:01.330
This guy is here to poach him again,
isn't he?

03:01.430 --> 03:02.560
And who is this?

03:03.190 --> 03:04.390
Using a honey trap?

03:04.590 --> 03:06.030
Isn't this going too far?

03:06.030 --> 03:07.590
-He's playing dirty.
-It's disgusting.

03:07.590 --> 03:08.680
What kind of behavior is this?

03:08.680 --> 03:09.960
It's just a honey trap.

03:09.960 --> 03:11.310
If he can do it, so can we.

03:11.310 --> 03:13.240
-What?
-How?

03:13.710 --> 03:14.800
Don't you think

03:14.820 --> 03:16.890
Ms. Lin is a better match for Coach?

03:20.150 --> 03:21.960
You mean...

03:21.960 --> 03:23.960
Even a hero cannot resist a beauty!

03:25.520 --> 03:27.310
Interesting!

03:27.310 --> 03:28.079
Let's ask him out tomorrow.

03:28.079 --> 03:30.800
-Okay!
-You've made progress, kid.

03:32.710 --> 03:35.430
Let's go find him
first thing tomorrow morning.

03:33.120 --> 03:37.280
[Feiyang Fried Skewers]

03:35.430 --> 03:37.290
-Let's eat first.
-Eat up. Eat up.

04:29.310 --> 04:31.440
You were tricked into coming here too?

04:31.630 --> 04:34.030
You came
even though you knew it was a trick?

04:34.190 --> 04:35.120
Ms. Lin, Coach!

04:35.120 --> 04:36.630
Coach, we're late.

04:40.159 --> 04:40.920
Qin Ao,

04:40.920 --> 04:42.190
you said it was an emergency.

04:42.190 --> 04:43.920
What kind of emergency is this?

04:44.040 --> 04:45.500
A movie ticket emergency.

04:45.510 --> 04:46.830
Boss won a prize at the arcade.

04:46.150 --> 04:47.820
[Poly Wanhe Cinema]

04:46.850 --> 04:48.110
He won 2 movie tickets.

04:50.000 --> 04:50.720
They came

04:50.720 --> 04:51.600
with flowers?

04:52.390 --> 04:54.040
Exactly.

04:54.750 --> 04:55.310
Coach.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.560
Take the tissues.

04:57.720 --> 04:58.600
Take them.

04:59.040 --> 05:00.480
I heard this movie is very touching.

05:00.480 --> 05:02.050
If Ms. Lin cries,

05:02.220 --> 05:03.710
you can wipe her tears.

05:04.630 --> 05:07.000
Qin Ao, you're really going for it.

05:09.040 --> 05:10.190
Go and watch the movie!

05:10.190 --> 05:11.870
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

05:11.870 --> 05:13.430
Let's go, Ms. Lin, Coach.

05:13.430 --> 05:15.040
Let's go.

05:15.480 --> 05:16.430
Take it.

05:16.430 --> 05:17.230
Ticket check.

05:17.560 --> 05:18.120
Okay.

05:18.120 --> 05:19.320
Check their tickets.

05:22.830 --> 05:23.480
I'm sorry.

05:23.480 --> 05:25.280
These are tickets for tomorrow.

05:26.270 --> 05:27.270
Lin Lu, what did you do?

05:27.270 --> 05:28.600
Wait. How can they be for tomorrow?

05:28.600 --> 05:30.560
-What? Weren't you the one who bought them?
-Who bought them?

05:30.560 --> 05:31.190
-You got them.
-You bought them.

05:31.190 --> 05:32.600
Who bought them?

05:32.600 --> 05:34.750
-Didn't you check when you bought them?
-Come on.

05:34.750 --> 05:36.880
-Did you buy them?
-Alright, alright.

05:37.430 --> 05:39.430
Since we're already out here,

05:40.000 --> 05:42.000
to repay your kindness,

05:42.000 --> 05:44.600
I'll treat you to late-night snacks
at the nearby night market.

05:44.600 --> 05:45.730
Late-night snacks!

05:46.430 --> 05:47.240
Let's go!

05:47.260 --> 05:48.310
Let's go!

05:53.510 --> 05:54.630
Does this look good?

05:54.630 --> 05:55.510
It looks good.

05:56.159 --> 05:57.480
With so many people,
let's get a bigger one.

05:57.480 --> 05:58.320
Sure.

05:58.400 --> 05:59.710
-The yellow one.
-We have 11 people eating.

05:59.710 --> 06:01.360
-I want to eat it.
-Come on.

06:01.360 --> 06:03.270
There are two skewers left.
One for each of you.

06:03.270 --> 06:04.510
It's quite good.

06:05.950 --> 06:07.160
The seasoning isn't as good as ours.

06:07.160 --> 06:08.630
This is really tasty.

06:08.630 --> 06:10.430
You don't have stinky tofu.

06:10.430 --> 06:11.630
Then don't eat at our shop next time.

06:11.630 --> 06:12.750
Fine, I won't.

06:12.750 --> 06:13.510
Last time I ate at your shop,

06:13.510 --> 06:15.040
I had diarrhea for days.

06:15.430 --> 06:17.310
Don't forget our mission today.

06:18.510 --> 06:19.070
I won't forget.

06:19.070 --> 06:19.770
Of course.

06:20.510 --> 06:22.190
By the way, where are they?

06:22.210 --> 06:23.610
-Right.
-Where are they?

06:25.070 --> 06:26.830
There.

06:26.830 --> 06:27.780
Let's go.

06:27.810 --> 06:28.750
Let's go.

06:30.360 --> 06:31.190
Ms. Lin!

06:31.190 --> 06:32.190
-Coach.
-Ms. Lin.

06:32.750 --> 06:33.870
Look what they are.

06:34.270 --> 06:35.460
Glow sticks!

06:35.630 --> 06:36.950
Here, one for each of you.

06:36.950 --> 06:37.430
Give me one.

06:37.430 --> 06:38.070
A white one.

06:38.070 --> 06:38.510
Get one for me.

06:38.510 --> 06:39.720
And these hats.

06:39.870 --> 06:40.630
Put these on,

06:40.630 --> 06:42.830
and you'll be the coolest guys tonight.

06:44.510 --> 06:45.950
I am cool even without it.

06:46.870 --> 06:49.159
Don't be so full of yourself, Qin Ao.

06:52.070 --> 06:53.130
It's a puppet show.

06:54.270 --> 06:54.830
Let's see what he is playing.

06:54.830 --> 06:57.240
He bestowed a precious sword on me

06:57.240 --> 07:01.830
to slay demons.

07:02.310 --> 07:03.870
Those demons

07:04.630 --> 07:07.830
are endless.

07:10.190 --> 07:11.870
I want to play marbles!

07:11.870 --> 07:13.950
-Me too!
-Me too!

07:18.920 --> 07:20.250
There's a wishing tree.

07:29.360 --> 07:31.240
Where should I hang it?

07:31.920 --> 07:33.390
Pass every exam?

07:35.270 --> 07:37.830
Kids nowadays are so competitive.

07:38.250 --> 07:39.580
I'll hang mine here too.

07:43.210 --> 07:45.280
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

07:45.750 --> 07:48.120
♪ On the summer night ♪

07:47.510 --> 07:48.870
Fifty points.

07:48.610 --> 07:54.120
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

07:50.560 --> 07:51.580
Look, look.

07:55.640 --> 07:57.900
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

07:58.610 --> 08:04.400
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

08:01.870 --> 08:03.200
What wish did you write?

08:03.750 --> 08:06.170
Good health and happiness every day.

08:06.310 --> 08:07.720
So unoriginal.

08:07.780 --> 08:13.200
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

08:10.560 --> 08:12.130
It's simple but sincere.

08:13.930 --> 08:19.730
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

08:14.670 --> 08:15.380
Alright.

08:20.150 --> 08:22.450
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

08:22.750 --> 08:24.640
Why don't we run

08:23.110 --> 08:28.930
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

08:24.720 --> 08:26.380
while they're playing games?

08:30.890 --> 08:32.159
[May all the members shine brightly]

08:32.179 --> 08:33.299
[Be healthy and happy every day]

08:32.179 --> 08:34.140
♪ Every night ♪

08:34.929 --> 08:37.039
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

08:37.799 --> 08:39.710
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

08:40.200 --> 08:42.890
♪ I follow the beat of my heart ♪

08:43.580 --> 08:46.200
♪ Like dust floating in the air ♪

08:47.180 --> 08:48.980
♪ Because of your love ♪

08:49.870 --> 08:54.430
♪ I shine brilliantly ♪

09:15.730 --> 09:17.800
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

09:18.270 --> 09:20.640
♪ On the summer night ♪

09:21.110 --> 09:26.620
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

09:23.320 --> 09:25.720
They shouldn't have noticed, should they?

09:26.870 --> 09:29.200
Bratty kids. They are so unreliable.

09:29.870 --> 09:30.960
Just let them play.

09:32.390 --> 09:33.200
Ms. Lin.

09:35.360 --> 09:36.700
I have a gift for you.

09:36.870 --> 09:37.720
What is it?

09:39.270 --> 09:40.670
Hold out your hand first.

09:51.390 --> 09:52.870
Your wish is

09:52.890 --> 09:55.410
that all team members shine brightly.

09:56.870 --> 09:57.840
But I think

09:59.750 --> 10:02.010
there is another person who also shines.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.800
Stars are supposed

10:13.830 --> 10:15.240
to shine on their own.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.550
This glow stick—

10:25.550 --> 10:28.010
my grandpa also gave me one
when I was little.

10:29.150 --> 10:31.150
I didn't expect you to be so playful.

10:31.550 --> 10:32.630
Thank you.

10:32.630 --> 10:34.030
I really like this gift.

10:50.870 --> 10:52.910
Wanxing, slow down.

10:56.790 --> 10:58.120
So agile.

10:58.630 --> 11:00.030
-Going up again?
-Yeah.

11:00.030 --> 11:01.030
I want to do it.

11:01.030 --> 11:02.510
Okay, be careful.

11:05.840 --> 11:07.030
Okay.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.550
I'm up here!

11:10.270 --> 11:11.670
Don't hold me.

11:11.670 --> 11:13.270
I'm not.

11:13.270 --> 11:14.960
Wanxing, hurry up
and finish that spicy strip.

11:14.960 --> 11:16.030
Otherwise, if we bring the smell home,

11:16.030 --> 11:17.200
we'll both get scolded.

11:17.200 --> 11:19.000
No, I want to stay here a little longer.

11:19.000 --> 11:19.360
Alright.

11:19.360 --> 11:20.030
Don't move.

11:20.030 --> 11:21.030
It's dangerous. Stay still.

11:21.030 --> 11:21.480
Wait a minute.

11:21.480 --> 11:23.480
Wait. Let me help you.

11:23.480 --> 11:24.670
There's no problem. Be brave.

11:24.670 --> 11:25.670
I've got you.

11:26.390 --> 11:27.670
I've got you.

11:27.670 --> 11:28.530
I'm right here.

11:30.030 --> 11:32.470
Nice! You made it over, didn't you?

11:32.470 --> 11:33.870
Just keep walking forward.

11:33.870 --> 11:35.030
Don't look to the sides.

11:35.030 --> 11:36.000
You're too naughty.

11:36.000 --> 11:37.030
You can't do it anymore?

11:37.030 --> 11:37.870
Alright, alright.

11:37.870 --> 11:39.070
Let me carry you down.

11:39.630 --> 11:41.630
I will always catch you.

11:58.910 --> 11:59.710
What's wrong?

12:04.390 --> 12:05.150
Nothing.

12:06.750 --> 12:08.030
I just thought

12:09.270 --> 12:11.480
no one would catch me like this again.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.120
Ms. Lin...

12:21.270 --> 12:22.510
Actually, I...

12:23.880 --> 12:24.590
I...

12:35.000 --> 12:35.750
Hello?

12:36.480 --> 12:38.600
Wang Fa, there's news.

12:38.600 --> 12:40.120
We found some clues.

12:42.480 --> 12:43.200
Okay.

12:49.760 --> 12:50.640
It's Felix Yu.

13:05.000 --> 13:06.390
Ms. Lin, Coach!

13:10.000 --> 13:10.750
Guys!

13:10.750 --> 13:12.510
Ms. Lin and Coach are missing.

13:12.630 --> 13:14.630
They disappeared together, right?

13:16.030 --> 13:17.960
-That's a good thing.
-Never mind.

13:19.690 --> 13:23.200
-Look how excited you are.
-Even playing games feels more exciting now, bros.

13:23.200 --> 13:24.510
Here I come!

13:24.510 --> 13:25.750
Look at your score.

13:26.630 --> 13:30.150
Six years ago, Ronald played Newton
in the Youth Super League semi-finals.

13:30.150 --> 13:31.640
Ronald suffered an upset loss.

13:31.640 --> 13:32.360
Why?

13:32.360 --> 13:33.790
Because their star forward,

13:33.790 --> 13:34.750
Larry Gilbert,

13:34.750 --> 13:36.000
suddenly had a medical issue

13:36.000 --> 13:37.860
and couldn't continue the match.

13:38.870 --> 13:42.150
Three years ago, Borton played Torson
in the Youth Super League

13:42.150 --> 13:45.510
quarter-finals. It was another upset loss
for the stronger team.

13:45.510 --> 13:46.630
The reason was exactly the same.

13:46.630 --> 13:48.390
Their key player, Tony Fields,

13:48.390 --> 13:49.240
had a sudden health problem

13:49.240 --> 13:50.970
and couldn't finish the match.

13:53.000 --> 13:53.820
Do you notice

13:54.270 --> 13:56.530
anything these two games have in common?

13:58.860 --> 14:01.920
Just like that match between
Nanton and Hammer back then—

14:01.920 --> 14:03.720
a strong team faced a weaker one,

14:04.630 --> 14:06.040
and it ended in an upset.

14:06.320 --> 14:09.240
And in every case,
the reason was the same: a key player

14:09.240 --> 14:10.810
suddenly ran into an unexpected problem.

14:10.810 --> 14:11.570
Exactly.

14:12.450 --> 14:14.510
This is the roster for these matches.

14:15.630 --> 14:16.820
I haven't looked closely yet.

14:16.820 --> 14:17.540
Here.

14:30.390 --> 14:32.110
Did you find any problems?

14:38.990 --> 14:41.590
[Kevin Lee]

14:44.860 --> 14:46.730
[Kevin Lee]

14:49.170 --> 14:52.870
[Profile]

14:54.750 --> 14:58.620
Newton, Torsen, Hammer—

14:59.120 --> 15:01.650
these 3 teams that pulled off upsets
back then

15:01.990 --> 15:04.190
all had an executive with the same name.

15:12.670 --> 15:13.390
Kevin Lee,

15:13.390 --> 15:15.480
the former manager of Hammer Club.

15:15.480 --> 15:16.750
Kevin Lee,

15:17.820 --> 15:19.550
former club manager...

15:20.270 --> 15:21.720
This person...

15:21.720 --> 15:23.680
does look a bit familiar.

15:31.040 --> 15:32.000
I've seen him.

15:32.970 --> 15:33.720
He is Chinese.

15:33.720 --> 15:35.270
Average capability.

15:35.270 --> 15:37.530
I don't have much of an impression of him.

15:37.640 --> 15:39.510
And the time he left Hammer

15:39.510 --> 15:41.260
was shortly after Jason's accident.

15:41.260 --> 15:42.560
Is it really such a coincidence?

15:42.560 --> 15:43.890
It's not a coincidence.

15:45.840 --> 15:48.500
Tell the people in the UK
to keep investigating.

15:49.510 --> 15:50.670
Kevin Lee?

16:11.290 --> 16:13.000
Take a look at Lin Lu's snapshot.

16:13.000 --> 16:15.150
A secretly taken photo, to be precise.

16:27.010 --> 16:29.350
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

16:29.990 --> 16:34.240
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

16:34.830 --> 16:36.790
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

16:37.310 --> 16:42.210
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
we met by chance ♪

16:40.350 --> 16:42.150
We look good.

16:42.800 --> 16:45.600
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

16:46.120 --> 16:49.540
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

16:50.510 --> 16:53.530
♪ I once dreamed of beauty ♪

16:54.190 --> 16:58.310
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

16:58.990 --> 17:01.530
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

17:01.990 --> 17:06.230
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

17:06.700 --> 17:09.609
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

17:08.859 --> 17:13.369
[Superstar Slacker]

17:10.119 --> 17:14.030
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

17:12.020 --> 17:15.230
Were you trying to say something
at the end today?

17:15.460 --> 17:17.500
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

17:18.240 --> 17:21.990
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

17:23.290 --> 17:25.710
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

17:24.000 --> 17:29.060
[Winfred]

17:24.510 --> 17:25.839
I'll tell you next time.

17:26.099 --> 17:27.560
That's a paid question.

17:26.380 --> 17:30.090
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

17:30.950 --> 17:33.480
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

17:34.270 --> 17:38.040
♪ Let the ending remain with
questions unanswered ♪

17:38.110 --> 17:39.790
What will he say to me?

17:38.840 --> 17:41.270
♪ No need to prove it with promises ♪

17:42.390 --> 17:45.900
♪ The dusk when we once vowed
to stay together ♪

17:47.610 --> 17:48.740
Pass it, pass it!

17:48.870 --> 17:50.180
Pass it here!

17:50.860 --> 17:51.890
Go, go, go!

17:52.090 --> 17:53.550
-Go back!
-Good ball!

17:55.070 --> 17:56.530
Someone's behind you! Go!

17:57.440 --> 17:58.480
Good ball!

18:02.510 --> 18:03.270
Pass it back if there's no chance.

18:03.270 --> 18:04.280
Pass it back!

18:04.590 --> 18:07.390
Chen Jianghe,
watch your passing angle and power!

18:07.590 --> 18:08.880
Ao, here!

18:11.310 --> 18:12.720
Pass it back, Qin Ao!

18:13.240 --> 18:15.240
It's fine, it's fine. Take the kick.

18:16.230 --> 18:17.550
It's okay. Let's try again.

18:17.550 --> 18:18.640
That was a pity.

18:18.640 --> 18:20.100
-Create chances.
-My bad.

18:22.070 --> 18:23.480
Go, go, go! Move forward!

18:25.310 --> 18:26.720
Defenders, spread out!

18:26.720 --> 18:28.230
Fall back, fall back!

18:33.200 --> 18:35.370
-Pass forward!
-There's a chance.

18:35.550 --> 18:37.030
Attack!

18:40.880 --> 18:42.350
Good shot, Boss!

18:46.310 --> 18:48.750
Good shot!

18:51.750 --> 18:53.680
-Coach!
-Coach!

18:53.680 --> 18:54.480
How was that?

18:54.480 --> 18:56.110
Not bad, but it's only the first half.

18:56.110 --> 18:57.440
Okay? Save your energy.

18:59.200 --> 19:00.550
Did you see my pass?

19:00.550 --> 19:02.790
-Coach, was that cool or what?
-Coach.

19:02.790 --> 19:04.350
Did you see it? Did you see it?

19:04.350 --> 19:05.950
Cool, cool. I saw it, I saw it.

19:09.510 --> 19:11.000
I'll talk to you later.

19:12.240 --> 19:13.770
I didn't even see it coming.

19:21.210 --> 19:24.210
Coaching the Hongjing No. 8 High School
football team

19:24.350 --> 19:25.750
and watching them play—

19:27.240 --> 19:28.070
Wang Fa,

19:29.200 --> 19:31.240
you are really living a good life.

19:34.070 --> 19:35.030
Jason wasn't

19:35.030 --> 19:36.030
as lucky as them.

19:37.680 --> 19:40.140
He will never
be able to play football again.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.490
About what happened to Jason,

19:51.510 --> 19:52.970
I'm still investigating.

19:54.200 --> 19:55.680
You don't have to pretend to feel guilty

19:55.680 --> 19:57.160
and investigate anymore.

20:00.350 --> 20:01.400
It's been a year,

20:02.030 --> 20:03.350
and I finally had the courage to open

20:03.350 --> 20:04.310
Jason's belongings.

20:04.310 --> 20:06.740
That was when I realized how much my son

20:07.200 --> 20:08.930
suffered while he was with you!

20:10.670 --> 20:12.020
See for yourself

20:12.590 --> 20:14.400
who really killed him.

20:18.280 --> 20:20.540
[Yang Mingsen]

20:23.130 --> 20:23.640
[Yang Mingsen]

20:23.690 --> 20:24.420
[I bought ice cream on my way back.]

20:24.440 --> 20:25.470
[Although my coach has strict requirements
for my body fat and doesn't let me eat sweets.]

20:25.490 --> 20:26.810
[Forget it. I'll just listen to him.
Next time, I'll try to hold myself back.]

20:27.020 --> 20:27.520
[I couldn't take it anymore and got into
a fight with them. A bunch of cowards]

20:27.540 --> 20:28.160
[who only bully people weaker than them.
I ended up scraping my arm.]

20:28.180 --> 20:29.000
[Luckily, Coach took me to the hospital.]

20:29.790 --> 20:30.510
[London is a little deserted at 2 a.m.
There aren't many cars or people.]

20:34.570 --> 20:37.390
[I was expelled.
Why doesn't even my coach believe me?]

20:40.900 --> 20:47.140
[I was expelled.
Why doesn't even my coach believe me?]

20:51.720 --> 20:53.340
You were Jason's coach,

20:54.000 --> 20:55.730
the person he trusted the most.

20:56.240 --> 20:57.680
But do you deserve it?

20:58.960 --> 21:00.680
Do you deserve his trust?

21:02.380 --> 21:04.110
What you did back then—

21:05.000 --> 21:07.930
how was it different
from pushing him down yourself?

21:09.880 --> 21:10.850
Do you think

21:12.920 --> 21:14.980
you are still qualified to be a coach?

21:40.790 --> 21:44.630
Good shot! Awesome!

21:52.990 --> 21:55.000
Coach, it was such a pity
you had to leave early

21:55.000 --> 21:56.830
-this afternoon.
-Yeah.

21:56.830 --> 21:57.880
You missed us scoring

21:57.880 --> 21:59.610
2 more goals in the second half.

22:01.540 --> 22:05.660
[Little Savage Tribe]

22:31.060 --> 22:32.140
Coach.

22:34.530 --> 22:36.340
I really can't hold on anymore.

22:37.050 --> 22:38.490
Pain

22:38.520 --> 22:40.260
is the price of growth.

22:44.790 --> 22:46.300
The mistake has been made.

22:46.320 --> 22:48.180
There is no point in running away.

22:48.320 --> 22:49.990
Come to me after you calm down,

22:50.010 --> 22:52.270
and we will talk about your future plans.

22:58.380 --> 22:59.940
I was expelled.

22:59.960 --> 23:02.080
Why doesn't even my coach believe me?

23:21.260 --> 23:24.110
Yesterday's friendly match
seemed very exciting.

23:24.110 --> 23:27.720
It's a pity I had a group meeting
in the afternoon and couldn't watch it.

23:27.720 --> 23:28.640
Nice ball!

23:29.680 --> 23:33.170
Did you leave in the second half
because you had something to do?

23:33.170 --> 23:33.890
Nice ball!

23:34.790 --> 23:35.350
Feng Suo, pass it to me!

23:35.350 --> 23:36.280
I'll pass to you!

23:37.070 --> 23:37.790
Nice ball!

23:40.270 --> 23:41.470
Yu Ming, pass it to me!

23:42.440 --> 23:43.310
Time's up.

23:43.750 --> 23:45.150
Take a ten-minute break.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.920
Why does something feel weird?

23:46.920 --> 23:47.640
Coach,

23:47.640 --> 23:49.110
can we beat Yinxiang now?

23:49.110 --> 23:49.510
Of course!

23:49.510 --> 23:51.720
-Of course!
-Of course. Easy peasy!

23:59.270 --> 24:00.200
Ms. Lin,

24:00.600 --> 24:01.460
this is for you.

24:02.540 --> 24:06.440
[Coach Manual]

24:05.510 --> 24:06.350
This is the team's

24:06.350 --> 24:07.880
training plan for the next month.

24:06.440 --> 24:08.290
[Weekly Football Training Plan]

24:08.590 --> 24:10.720
If you want to go further in the league,

24:11.030 --> 24:13.200
you have to
spend more time and energy practicing.

24:13.200 --> 24:14.880
A month's training plan?

24:15.960 --> 24:17.820
Why give it to me so far in advance?

24:21.340 --> 24:22.340
I...

24:22.840 --> 24:24.120
will be leaving soon.

24:26.000 --> 24:27.370
-What do you mean?
-Leave?

24:27.370 --> 24:28.550
-Leave?
-Leave?

24:28.730 --> 24:29.940
Where are you going?

24:29.970 --> 24:31.970
Are you going to Yongchuan Hengjiu?

24:37.590 --> 24:38.590
Really?

24:43.160 --> 24:45.020
I have to give them a final answer.

25:02.050 --> 25:02.850
Coach,

25:03.750 --> 25:05.350
is this your final decision?

25:16.550 --> 25:18.330
When do you plan to leave then?

25:20.340 --> 25:20.960
Tomorrow.

25:20.980 --> 25:21.970
Tomorrow?

25:22.000 --> 25:23.200
-So soon?
-Tomorrow?

25:24.350 --> 25:26.310
Did they offer you a high salary?

25:26.310 --> 25:27.310
You can tell me.

25:27.310 --> 25:28.590
Maybe I can apply for this fund

25:28.590 --> 25:29.790
from the school.

25:29.790 --> 25:30.830
15 million.

25:32.750 --> 25:34.750
This is Yongchuan Hengjiu's offer.

25:35.270 --> 25:37.060
That much?

25:37.790 --> 25:38.830
15 million?

25:38.830 --> 25:39.960
That's way too much.

26:42.320 --> 26:44.210
When I was sick,

26:44.240 --> 26:45.890
I thought I heard you say

26:46.500 --> 26:47.500
you won't leave.

26:52.460 --> 26:53.310
Sorry.

26:57.480 --> 27:00.010
I must have been delirious
and heard it wrong.

27:04.120 --> 27:05.380
I will settle the rent.

27:05.610 --> 27:07.740
Felix Yu will handle the moving for me.

27:07.880 --> 27:08.800
No rush.

27:09.400 --> 27:11.000
What if you come back?

27:16.260 --> 27:17.330
Lin Wanxing.

27:19.450 --> 27:20.650
You were right.

27:24.790 --> 27:25.960
I don't belong here.

27:27.490 --> 27:28.650
I'm just a passerby.

27:34.550 --> 27:35.480
I'll go up first.

28:24.980 --> 28:30.470
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

28:31.100 --> 28:35.680
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

28:37.470 --> 28:42.820
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

28:43.570 --> 28:49.350
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

28:45.960 --> 28:47.070
You were right.

28:49.510 --> 28:50.680
I don't belong here.

28:50.610 --> 28:56.420
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

28:52.590 --> 28:53.980
I'm just a passerby.

28:55.640 --> 28:57.950
Everyone has the right to choose.

28:57.210 --> 29:02.030
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

28:58.830 --> 29:00.720
But what about the kids?

29:01.740 --> 29:03.130
What will they do?

29:03.640 --> 29:09.080
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

29:08.830 --> 29:09.950
Ms. Lin.

29:09.940 --> 29:14.890
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

29:11.350 --> 29:12.550
I don't have

29:13.310 --> 29:15.040
many chances left in this life.

29:15.310 --> 29:18.440
We've always been abandoned anyway.

29:15.960 --> 29:21.740
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

29:19.270 --> 29:20.830
We're used to it.

29:20.830 --> 29:22.640
Only a fool wouldn't know how to choose.

29:22.570 --> 29:28.140
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

29:22.750 --> 29:24.830
It's normal to give up on us.

29:24.830 --> 29:26.410
We really have nothing.

29:26.850 --> 29:28.670
Playing football is the only way

29:28.720 --> 29:30.340
we can prove ourselves.

29:29.010 --> 29:34.620
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

29:30.550 --> 29:31.420
Coach.

29:31.440 --> 29:32.980
We have something for you.

29:33.110 --> 29:34.720
Such an important thing—

29:35.480 --> 29:40.720
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

29:36.110 --> 29:37.400
I'll keep it for you.

29:37.400 --> 29:39.070
Great!

29:39.070 --> 29:40.000
We now have

29:40.000 --> 29:41.240
a world-class coach too!

29:41.240 --> 29:42.880
And he's from Nanton!

29:42.030 --> 29:47.360
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

29:44.460 --> 29:45.910
Lin Wanxing.

29:46.680 --> 29:49.530
You gave them a fragile hope.

29:48.100 --> 29:53.840
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

29:50.180 --> 29:51.510
But now,

29:52.320 --> 29:54.190
you're letting Wang Fa leave,

29:54.220 --> 29:56.590
shattering this hope.

29:54.620 --> 30:00.270
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

29:57.250 --> 29:59.490
Do you want to see

29:59.520 --> 30:02.080
them abandoned again?

30:01.270 --> 30:06.970
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

30:08.200 --> 30:12.710
♪ Take away my reflection ♪

30:14.560 --> 30:21.620
♪ And go in search of distant scenery ♪

31:14.850 --> 31:17.510
See you
on the tutoring center's rooftop later.

31:19.000 --> 31:20.500
[See you
on the tutoring center's rooftop later.]

31:20.500 --> 31:23.870
[No, thanks. I...]

31:23.890 --> 31:25.190
[One last meal.]

31:24.270 --> 31:25.350
One last meal

31:29.160 --> 31:30.590
to send you off,

31:30.590 --> 31:31.400
okay?

31:37.450 --> 31:40.930
[To send you off, okay?]

31:40.960 --> 31:43.630
[Okay.]

31:43.030 --> 31:43.830
Okay.

32:13.160 --> 32:14.530
Coming!

32:14.560 --> 32:15.770
Start recording.

32:16.800 --> 32:18.230
Come on, Chen Jianghe.

32:18.250 --> 32:19.590
Chen Jianghe, say something.

32:19.590 --> 32:20.160
Don't film me.

32:20.160 --> 32:21.110
Your boss is waiting to be filmed.

32:21.110 --> 32:21.610
Come on.

32:21.640 --> 32:22.720
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

32:22.720 --> 32:23.750
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

32:23.750 --> 32:25.280
Look at the camera, Ms. Lin.

32:25.750 --> 32:26.590
What are you filming?

32:26.590 --> 32:29.480
I'm just recording our cooking moments.

32:30.310 --> 32:31.350
Is it okay to grill it like this?

32:31.350 --> 32:32.720
Be careful. Don't hurt your hands.

32:32.720 --> 32:34.830
-Alright, stop filming me.
-The vegetables are washed.

32:34.830 --> 32:36.240
Put them there, Master Zhi Hui.

32:36.240 --> 32:37.790
-Be careful.
-I look cool in this shot.

32:37.790 --> 32:39.200
This is called skill.

32:41.070 --> 32:42.440
-Stop filming and come help.
-Give it to me.

32:42.440 --> 32:42.920
Go help them.

32:42.920 --> 32:43.790
Coming.

32:43.790 --> 32:44.400
I'll be there after this shot.

32:44.400 --> 32:45.800
I am the cameraman today.

32:47.460 --> 32:49.310
Is there anything I can help with?

32:49.310 --> 32:51.110
I... don't think so.

32:51.590 --> 32:52.400
Coach needs help skewering shrimp.

32:52.400 --> 32:53.550
Really cool indeed.

32:53.550 --> 32:54.880
Turn up the brightness.

32:55.550 --> 32:56.830
Qin Ao, that's enough.

32:56.830 --> 32:57.720
Hurry up and come help.

32:57.720 --> 32:58.550
Coming.

32:58.550 --> 32:59.920
I'm being a model here.

33:00.690 --> 33:01.480
Qin Ao.

33:01.480 --> 33:02.790
Got it. Coming.

33:02.790 --> 33:04.720
Who cut these veggies? Good knife skills.

33:04.720 --> 33:05.400
Look at the camera.

33:05.400 --> 33:07.160
The students are all quite happy.

33:07.160 --> 33:08.160
Be careful.

33:08.200 --> 33:09.730
It's a rare chance to relax.

33:11.200 --> 33:12.730
Have you finished packing?

33:13.540 --> 33:14.870
I don't have much stuff.

33:30.200 --> 33:31.000
By the way.

33:32.280 --> 33:34.280
Are you taking the high-speed rail?

33:34.510 --> 33:35.480
I remember

33:35.480 --> 33:37.900
the last train to Yongchuan is at 9:30.

33:38.350 --> 33:39.640
Will you be late?

33:43.200 --> 33:44.270
No need to rush.

33:44.640 --> 33:46.040
Someone is picking me up.

33:48.270 --> 33:49.160
Makes sense.

33:50.160 --> 33:52.020
Qin Ao, you are just making a mess.

33:56.640 --> 33:57.550
Don't drink too fast.

33:57.550 --> 33:58.950
You'll get drunk easily.

34:02.830 --> 34:04.350
Then let me get drunk.

34:11.070 --> 34:11.760
Boss.

34:11.760 --> 34:12.550
Should we

34:12.550 --> 34:14.280
record something as a final souvenir?

34:14.280 --> 34:15.110
Sure.

34:15.110 --> 34:16.030
Ms. Lin.

34:17.840 --> 34:19.000
Let's play a game.

34:19.840 --> 34:20.880
What game?

34:20.880 --> 34:23.110
The rule is someone gets blindfolded
and tries to catch others.

34:23.110 --> 34:24.480
The rest will hide.

34:24.480 --> 34:25.480
Then the catcher

34:25.480 --> 34:27.590
has to guess who they caught.

34:27.590 --> 34:29.389
You pass only if you guess right.

34:29.760 --> 34:32.190
Okay. Who will be blindfolded first?

34:34.550 --> 34:35.969
-Let's have Coach be the first one.
-Let's have Coach be the first one.

34:35.969 --> 34:36.840
Coach.

34:36.840 --> 34:37.880
-Coach.
-Coach.

34:37.880 --> 34:38.880
Coach!

34:38.880 --> 34:39.840
-Coach.
-No problem.

34:39.840 --> 34:43.710
-Coach! Coach!
-Let's hide.

34:45.510 --> 34:48.000
The hexagram shows
Coach will definitely guess right.

34:48.000 --> 34:49.199
Tie it tighter, Boss.

34:49.510 --> 34:50.800
You can't see now, right?

34:50.800 --> 34:53.070
Come on, it's starting!

34:53.070 --> 34:58.840
-Five, four, three, two, one.
-Don't hide here!

35:05.710 --> 35:07.030
Come here.

35:07.110 --> 35:08.840
Come catch me.

35:08.840 --> 35:10.830
I'm Ms. Lin.

35:31.010 --> 35:31.830
Guess who I am.

35:34.800 --> 35:36.510
I felt a pimple.

35:36.760 --> 35:37.580
Um...

35:38.190 --> 35:39.050
Zheng Feiyang!

35:39.230 --> 35:40.760
Coach, I'm over here!

35:40.810 --> 35:42.210
You got the wrong person!

35:43.320 --> 35:43.840
Qin Ao?

35:43.840 --> 35:44.800
Wrong again.

35:50.920 --> 35:52.030
What are you doing?

35:52.800 --> 35:54.120
Guess.

35:56.030 --> 35:56.840
Qin Ao.

35:58.400 --> 35:59.670
You're bad at this, Qin Ao.

35:59.670 --> 36:01.550
Why?

36:01.550 --> 36:03.350
Your hair is too spiky, you know?

36:04.480 --> 36:05.960
Your hair is too spiky!

36:05.960 --> 36:08.030
Let's take a group photo together.

36:08.030 --> 36:09.360
-Okay.
-Let's go.

36:09.360 --> 36:10.490
-Come on.
-Let's go.

36:11.710 --> 36:12.550
Coach.

36:15.680 --> 36:17.190
Coach, Ms. Lin,
you guys stand in the middle.

36:17.190 --> 36:18.360
Come on.

36:18.800 --> 36:19.660
Come on, Coach.

36:21.800 --> 36:22.280
Get closer.

36:22.280 --> 36:23.410
Get a little closer.

36:24.320 --> 36:26.110
Three, two, one.

36:28.150 --> 36:28.760
Let's take another one.

36:28.760 --> 36:29.510
One more.

36:30.840 --> 36:31.510
Coach,

36:31.800 --> 36:32.430
smile.

36:36.100 --> 36:36.620
Okay.

36:38.880 --> 36:41.440
Three, two, one.

36:48.510 --> 36:50.710
Coach, does this photo look okay to you?

36:57.320 --> 36:58.320
It's pretty good.

36:58.870 --> 36:59.600
Send it to me.

37:04.670 --> 37:06.930
It's getting late. Go home now, you guys.

37:08.840 --> 37:10.920
-Bye, Coach.
-Bye, Coach.

37:10.920 --> 37:13.190
-Bye, Coach.
-Be careful.

37:13.400 --> 37:14.110
Bye, Coach.

37:14.110 --> 37:16.280
-Let's go. Let's go. Let's go.
-Bye, Coach.

37:16.280 --> 37:23.300
[Yuanyuan Tutoring Class]

37:17.000 --> 37:18.320
Goodbye, Coach.

37:36.360 --> 37:37.110
Coach.

37:38.470 --> 37:40.470
Are we not going to see you tomorrow?

37:59.010 --> 37:59.700
Coach,

38:00.630 --> 38:01.960
are you really leaving?

38:07.190 --> 38:08.030
Never mind.

38:08.760 --> 38:10.220
Just pretend I didn't ask.

38:11.550 --> 38:13.360
Thanks for your hard work recently, Coach.

38:13.360 --> 38:15.030
You must come back
and visit us when you have time.

38:15.030 --> 38:16.440
We will train hard.

38:16.440 --> 38:18.630
Don't forget to come watch
our next game, Coach.

38:18.630 --> 38:21.190
If you don't like Yongchuan Hengjiu,
just come back.

38:21.190 --> 38:23.360
Coach, thank you.

38:23.880 --> 38:24.800
Thank you.

38:24.800 --> 38:25.510
Coach.

38:26.320 --> 38:27.650
Please don't forget us.

38:47.550 --> 38:48.280
Coach!

38:49.510 --> 38:50.230
Coach!

38:51.130 --> 38:52.030
-Coach!
-Coach!

38:52.030 --> 38:52.430
Coach!

38:52.440 --> 38:53.470
-Coach!
-Coach!

38:53.510 --> 38:54.320
Coach!

38:54.340 --> 38:55.110
Coach!

39:05.960 --> 39:06.550
Coach.

39:31.110 --> 39:31.960
Goodbye.

39:34.020 --> 39:34.870
Goodbye.

39:37.630 --> 39:38.900
Bye, Coach.

39:39.230 --> 39:40.650
-Bye.
-Bye, Coach.

39:40.670 --> 39:42.580
-Bye, Coach.
-Bye, Coach.

39:46.640 --> 39:47.930
♪ Time's passing by ♪

39:48.590 --> 39:50.820
♪ Nothing remains ♪

39:51.570 --> 39:54.510
♪ All the dreamers awake alone ♪

39:53.440 --> 39:54.570
I'll go see them off.

39:54.840 --> 39:56.730
♪ Shadows above ♪

39:57.330 --> 39:59.470
♪ Rain falls around ♪

39:59.620 --> 40:00.820
♪ In your arms ♪

40:01.230 --> 40:02.850
♪ We become one ♪

40:03.500 --> 40:05.160
♪ Through day and night ♪

40:05.900 --> 40:08.270
♪ I can see you ♪

40:09.240 --> 40:11.480
♪ In my eyes ♪

40:12.200 --> 40:13.650
♪ Just hold me tight ♪

40:14.490 --> 40:19.830
♪ Look into my soul so deeply ♪

40:16.490 --> 40:20.030
[Wutong Road Bus Stop]

40:21.070 --> 40:22.470
♪ Rainbow sunlight ♪

40:23.210 --> 40:24.350
♪ Painful tears are gone ♪

40:25.520 --> 40:26.260
♪ Wonderful dreams ♪

40:27.270 --> 40:28.620
♪ Are so close to me ♪

40:29.940 --> 40:30.830
♪ Memories fly ♪

40:31.720 --> 40:32.970
♪ Leave them all behind ♪

40:33.990 --> 40:39.590
♪ Just take my hand and stay with me ♪

40:34.760 --> 40:36.380
What are you two crying for?

40:36.770 --> 40:38.300
Pull yourselves together.

40:38.360 --> 40:39.670
Aren't you crying too?

40:53.440 --> 40:55.000
Coach went to a better team.

40:56.030 --> 40:57.270
We should be happy for him.

40:57.270 --> 41:02.800
[Promote Civility
and Build a Better Society]

41:01.340 --> 41:02.490
Ms. Lin.

41:03.440 --> 41:04.730
Why are you such a wuss?

41:06.510 --> 41:07.950
You looked like

41:07.980 --> 41:09.820
a deserter just now.

41:10.760 --> 41:13.090
You're talking about yourselves, right?

41:15.150 --> 41:16.670
You're just too shy.

41:19.550 --> 41:20.400
Exactly.

41:20.920 --> 41:22.670
You definitely didn't say anything
to Coach like

41:22.670 --> 41:23.920
"Please stay,"

41:23.920 --> 41:25.440
or "Don't leave."

41:26.940 --> 41:28.440
You can't keep someone

41:28.750 --> 41:30.210
who really wants to leave.

41:35.350 --> 41:41.060
[Promote Civility
and Build a Better Society]

41:37.380 --> 41:38.730
Fifteen million...

41:39.400 --> 41:40.860
It's indeed a lot of money.

41:41.300 --> 41:42.360
But Coach is great.

41:43.360 --> 41:44.560
He's worth the price.

41:44.920 --> 41:45.880
One day,

41:47.320 --> 41:48.980
we'll have Coach see us again.

42:04.640 --> 42:05.390
Bye, Ms. Lin

42:05.410 --> 42:06.770
-See you.
-See you.

42:07.920 --> 42:08.710
Bye, Ms. Lin.

42:08.710 --> 42:09.510
Be careful.

42:09.600 --> 42:10.820
Ms. Lin.

42:11.150 --> 42:13.400
As for the new coach,
we can discuss it later.

42:13.400 --> 42:14.600
Don't worry about us.

42:15.450 --> 42:16.330
Bye-bye, Ms. Lin.

42:16.330 --> 42:17.520
-Be careful.
-Okay.

42:18.190 --> 42:19.150
By the way, Ms. Lin.

42:19.150 --> 42:21.510
We secretly recorded a short video
for Coach.

42:21.510 --> 42:22.360
The old camera

42:22.360 --> 42:23.960
is in the box
at the back of the classroom.

42:23.960 --> 42:25.190
You can record a clip later

42:25.190 --> 42:27.120
and edit it together to send to him.

42:27.190 --> 42:27.920
Go on now.

42:59.840 --> 43:00.710
Ms. Lin.

43:06.340 --> 43:11.410
[Wutong Road Bus Stop]

43:12.510 --> 43:14.030
You didn't come back for a while,

43:14.030 --> 43:15.560
so I came out to look for you.

43:17.320 --> 43:19.320
I just saw those brats off to the bus.

43:26.360 --> 43:29.090
[Love Makes Dreams Come True]

43:32.420 --> 43:34.500
Could you return this to them for me?

43:39.550 --> 43:41.680
This is a token of their appreciation.

43:41.680 --> 43:42.900
Just keep it.

43:43.750 --> 43:45.480
If you think it's too old

43:45.510 --> 43:46.840
and don't want to use it,

43:47.070 --> 43:48.200
just leave it there.

43:50.700 --> 43:52.160
It's not that it's too old.

43:54.030 --> 43:55.440
It's just that I'm no longer qualified
to keep it.

43:55.440 --> 43:56.240
[Love Makes Dreams Come True]

43:57.670 --> 44:00.270
Then why didn't you return it to them
yourself?

44:02.840 --> 44:04.070
I missed the chance,

44:06.000 --> 44:08.000
so I couldn't bring myself to say it.

44:11.370 --> 44:19.680
[Love Makes Dreams Come True]

44:22.150 --> 44:23.320
Actually,

44:26.670 --> 44:28.440
I still haven't given up hope.

44:29.590 --> 44:30.780
I always feel like

44:33.840 --> 44:35.020
you won't leave.

44:44.170 --> 44:45.060
Sorry.

44:51.320 --> 44:52.150
Ms. Lin.

44:55.890 --> 44:56.660
Goodbye.
